程序包 org.texttechnology.parliament_browser_6_4.data

接口 Member

  • 所有已知实现类:
    Member_Impl
    public interface Member
    Interface defining the contract for a Member entity within a parliamentary system. It outlines the basic properties and functions necessary to manage a member's information, including personal details, titles, and parliamentary service history.
